</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-177_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-178_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-179_ pf-heading-1-h3">The importance of basic life support (BLS) training</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Classroom_Basic_Life_Support_Training_Courses_Available_for_Immediate_Booking_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1727435214" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Classroom_Basic_Life_Support_Training_Courses_Available_for_Immediate_Booking_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1727435214 1536w" width="960" height="1440" alt="Classroom Basic Life Support Training Courses Available for Immediate Booking - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Classroom Basic Life Support Training Courses Available for Immediate Booking - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gdyfxU iluFjz pf-181_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-182_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by  LightFieldStudios via Envato Elements</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-184_ pf-heading-1-h3">What is BLS?</h3><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-186_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Basic Life Support (BLS) refers to a set of clinical interventions used to sustain life in emergencies, such as cardiac arrest, respiratory distress, or choking, until advanced medical care is available. BLS focuses on maintaining airway patency, supporting breathing and circulation, and recognising life-threatening emergencies.</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-188_ pf-heading-1-h3">Why is BLS training crucial?</h3><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-190_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Statistics show that in the UK, around 30,000 out-of-hospital cardiac arrests occur each year, with a survival rate of less than 10%. Immediate intervention with CPR (Cardiopulmonary Resuscitation) can double or even triple a victimâ€™s chances of survival. For healthcare professionals and social care providers, being proficient in BLS is not just a professional requirement but a societal imperative.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-192_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-193_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-194_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key facts and statistics</h3><img title="Join Our Basic Life Support Practical Training Courses in Westminster - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" alt="Join Our Basic Life Support Practical Training Courses in Westminster - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Innovation_A_Guide_to_Measuring_Success_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_ee69602d-1c85-4a76-a511-e0fd02aabb8a.jpg?v=1727437349" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Innovation_A_Guide_to_Measuring_Success_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_ee69602d-1c85-4a76-a511-e0fd02aabb8a.jpg?v=1727437349&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Innovation_A_Guide_to_Measuring_Success_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_ee69602d-1c85-4a76-a511-e0fd02aabb8a.jpg?v=1727437349&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Innovation_A_Guide_to_Measuring_Success_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_ee69602d-1c85-4a76-a511-e0fd02aabb8a.jpg?v=1727437349&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Innovation_A_Guide_to_Measuring_Success_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_ee69602d-1c85-4a76-a511-e0fd02aabb8a.jpg?v=1727437349&width=1200 1200w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Innovation_A_Guide_to_Measuring_Success_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_ee69602d-1c85-4a76-a511-e0fd02aabb8a.jpg?v=1727437349&width=1400 1400w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Innovation_A_Guide_to_Measuring_Success_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_ee69602d-1c85-4a76-a511-e0fd02aabb8a.jpg?v=1727437349&width=1600 1600w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Unlocking_Innovation_A_Guide_to_Measuring_Success_-